prodNameC: 拜爾斯達光學免疫法披衣菌測定試劑
ingredientsDesc:
Reagent 1A:
Extraction Reagent: pH 6.0 buffer solution containing dithioerythritol and a broad spectrum protease.
Reagent 1B:
Extraction Reagent: pH 13.0 buffer solution containing chenodeoxycholic acid.
Reagent 2:
neutralizer: pH 7.0 buffer solution containing guanidine-HCl preserved with 0.5% ProClin 300 Preservative.
Reagent 3:
Conjugae: pH 8.0 buffered protein solution containing anti (C. trachomatis) antibody (murine) conjugated to Horseradish peroxidase (HRP) and preserved with 0.5% ProClin 300 solution.
Reagent 4:
Wash Solution: pH 7.8 saline buffer preserved with 0.1% ProClin 300 preservative.
Substrate:
pH 5.5 aqueous solution of tetramethylbenzidine (TMB) and hydrogen peroxide.
Positive Control:
pH 7.0 protein solution containing inactivated C. trachomatis and preserved with 0.5% ProClin 300 preservative.
Test Devices:
Protein coated surface spotted with goat anti-moue IgG as a procedural control.
applicantAddr: 新北市永和區中山路一段174號11樓
efficacy: 檢測子宮頸內棉棒檢體中的披衣菌抗原。

mdKind.mdKindMCodeName: C 免疫學及微生物學用裝置
